# Exploration: od

## Rounds
  round 0: 324 isolated cumulative, 166 identical in round (single-phase)

## Observed: 18/21 flags
  11 solo, 7 via combination
  3 additional error-differentiated
  3 behavioral aliases detected
  robustness: 20 robust, 0 moderate, 0 fragile

Aliases: -A = --address-radix, -N = --read-bytes, -j = --skip-bytes, -t = --format, -v = --output-duplicates

